    {
      "id": "sybil_24_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_24",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This power unit utilizes six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a high-revving, linear power band. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip variable M differential lock. To ensure chassis longevity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the suspension geometry remains true with upgraded polyurethane bushings. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve shim adjustment and a cooling system overhaul. While the exterior shows minor signs of road use, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response are sharp, making this a prime example for an enthusiast seeking a tactile, high-performance machine.",
